sectionText: This course will open to all students in the College of Business on Monday, November 14, 2016 and to business minors on Monday, November 21, 2016 at approximately 9:00 a.m. This course will open to ISE and French Commercial students on Monday, November 28, 2016 at approximately 9:00 a.m.  This is an elective course for undergraduate students pursuing the business minor.
